Categories
==========

Categories are used to group similar pages together. Categories can belong to other categories,
giving a hierachical structure. Categoriescan also have their own content, such as this.

Usage
-----

Categories are made up of two parts: the listing of categories for a given page, and the content of
a category itself.

The list of of categories that a page belongs to are placed in a file under the 'categories' folder,
with the file named the same as the page. This file should contain a simple listing of the text
label for the category and the location of it, one per line. The format of each line is
<label>#url.

